PN,35101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784053121
OL,3,CFlight cancelled after passenger
OL,4,Caccidentally opens emergency exit
OL,6,FA flight from Manchester to Guernsey
OL,7,Fhad to be cancelled after a passenger
OL,8,Fopened an emergency exit.
OL,10,FThe GR679 service was scheduled to
OL,11,Fdepart at 7:05pm on Sunday (12 July)
OL,12,Fbut did not make it off the tarmac as
OL,13,Fthe plane was taken out of service
OL,14,Ffollowing the incident.
OL,16,FOperator Aurigny says "there was no
OL,17,Fmalicious intent" and it is "satisfied
OL,18,Fthat this was not deliberate but
OL,19,Frather accidental".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/2
