FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784053121
OL,3,CFlight cancelled after passenger
OL,4,Caccidentally opens emergency exit
OL,6,FHowever, the emergency exit must be
OL,7,Freset by a qualified engineer -
OL,8,Fmeaning that those on board faced an
OL,9,Fovernight stay in Manchester as there
OL,10,Fwere no services back to the island
OL,11,Flater that day.
OL,13,FNo one was injured and a flight on the
OL,14,Fsame route the following morning did
OL,15,Fdepart as scheduled.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the airline adds:
OL,18,F"Aurigny regrets the inconvenience
OL,19,Fcaused to passengers on this service
OL,20,Fby this unfortunate and unusual
OL,21,Fsituation."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/2
